3. Visual Analysis of Compound Properties

Ion Mass Frequency and Density

Distribution of nominal molecular masses (Da) for all filtered compounds. The blue bars represent the frequency count, and the red curve illustrates the estimated kernel density (KDE).

Superclass Distribution

Proportional distribution of compounds across the primary NPC Superclasses. Minor classes are grouped into 'Others' for clarity.

Class Distribution

Absolute counts for the twenty most abundant NPC Classes identified in the dataset, providing a more specific view of the chemical diversity.
